input.deliverable: Return a concrete section-by-section blueprint + exact Tailwind classes + component/file list to implement.

raw.instructions: Creative Director: luxury spacing/typography/rhythm. Output: section blueprint + tokens + component rules.

content.text:
Below is a concrete, mobileâfirst homepage blueprint for Dominat8 with exact Tailwind classes, design tokens, and component rules. Itâs optimized for fast load, ruralâprofessional tone, and âSiteGroundâlevel wow,â with luxury spacing/typography/rhythm. Includes a component/file list to implement. Keep the HOME_OK marker as specified.

Design tokens (Tailwind theme extensions)
- Color palette (earth + sky, high contrast, accessible)
  - primary: #386641 (evergreen)
  - primary-600: #2F5537
  - primary-700: #27472F
  - accent: #F59E0B (harvest amber)
  - sky: #C7E0FF -> #EAF3FF (hero top)
  - soil: #EDE7DD (warm light), #1E1E1B (charcoal)
  - neutral: #0B0B0A (ink), #6B7280 (muted), #F8FAFC (paper)
- Typography
  - Headings: âSource Serif 4â, Georgia, serif (fall back: ui-serif, Georgia)
  - Body/UI: âInterâ, system-ui, sans-serif (fallback: ui-sans-serif, system-ui)
  - Sizing:
    - h1: text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight tracking-tight
    - h2: text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-snug tracking-tight
    - h3: text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug
    - body: text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed
    - caption: text-sm leading-normal
- Spacing scale (luxury rhythm; base 4px)
  - Section Y: py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28
  - Block gap: space-y-6 md:space-y-8
  - Grid gap: gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10
- Radius + Shadows
  - rounded-xl on cards, rounded-2xl on hero media
  - shadow-lg/2xl with shadow-black/10; hover:shadow-amber/10 for accent
- Container rule
  - container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8
- Motion
  - transition-all duration-300 ease-out, prefers-reduced-motion: reduce

Suggested Tailwind config snippet (tailwind.config.{js,ts})
- theme.extend:
  - colors: primary: { DEFAULT: #386641, 600: #2F5537, 700: #27472F }, accent: #F59E0B, soil: { light: #EDE7DD, dark: #1E1E1B }, sky: { 100: #EAF3FF, 200: #C7E0FF }
  - boxShadow: { soft: '0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)' }
  - fontFamily: { serif: ['"Source Serif 4"', 'Georgia', 'serif'], sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'] }

Global component rules
- Body base classes: min-h-screen bg-white text-neutral-900 font-sans antialiased [font-feature-settings:'ss01','ss02'] selection:bg-primary/10 selection:text-primary-700
- Container utility: className="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
- Section utility: className="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28"
- Buttons
  - Primary: inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white px-5 py-3 md:px-6 md:py-3.5 text-base md:text-lg font-semibold shadow-soft hover:bg-primary-600 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary/40 active:translate-y-px transition-all
  - Secondary: inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-neutral-900 px-5 py-3 md:px-6 md:py-3.5 font-semibold hover:border-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary/20 transition-all
- Cards
  - Base: rounded-xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-neutral-200 shadow-soft hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all
  - Padding: p-6 md:p-8
- Icon circle
  - h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center

Section-by-section blueprint with exact Tailwind classes

0) HTML shell and fonts (fast load)
- Use system fonts by default; progressively enhance with font-display: swap. Self-host later if needed.
- Head performance:
  - <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  - <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossOrigin="" />
  - If using Google Fonts: Inter: wght@400;500;600;700 and Source Serif 4: wght@600;700
- Root element classes on <body>: "min-h-screen bg-white text-neutral-900 font-sans antialiased"

1) Header / Navigation (sticky, minimal)
- Wrapper: header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-neutral-100"
- Inner: div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 md:h-20 flex items-center justify-between"
- Left (brand):
  - a class="flex items-center gap-3" href="/"
    - span (logo placeholder) class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-primary text-white grid place-content-center font-semibold" -> âD8â
    - span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight" -> âDominat8â
- Center (desktop nav):
  - nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8"
    - a class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors" -> Solutions
    - a class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors" -> Industries
    - a class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors" -> Resources
    - a class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors" -> About
- Right:
  - div class="flex items-center gap-3"
    - a class="hidden md:inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900 hover:text-primary transition-colors" -> Sign in
    - a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold shadow-soft hover:bg-primary-600 transition-all" -> Book a call
    - button class="md:hidden inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors" aria-label="Open menu"
- Mobile menu panel (deferred or no-js):
  - div class="md:hidden border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white" hidden by default
  - ul class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 space-y-2"

2) Hero (wow gradient + rural imagery)

- Background: div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-200 via-white to-white" aria-hidden="true"
- Decorative (subtle noise): optional small data-uri or CSS
